title New Note Single Page App Sequence

# POSTing new note
browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
server-->browser: HTTP status 201, message: 'note created'

# refreshing page to see the new note
note over browser:
browser invokes redrawNotes() function
based on changed xhttp state change
making the new note appear
end note
